                     <h4 id="Content"><p>April 22, 2024 marks the 55th World Earth Day. This year's theme is "Planet vs. Plastics." Humans consume about 1 million plastic bottles every minute, and more than 5 trillion plastic bags are used each year. China's capacity and output of waste plastic recycling and regeneration both rank first in the world. Watch this video.</p>
